(1, 1, '2009-04-12 08:15:25', '2009-04-12 00:15:25', '<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 18pt;"><img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-25" title="e5ad99e4b8bde8908d-045_resize" src="http://herun/wp-content/uploads/2009/04/e5ad99e4b8bde8908d-045_resize-300x225.jpg" alt="e5ad99e4b8bde8908d-045_resize" width="300" height="225" /></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 18pt;"><!--more--></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 18pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">一、产品概述：</span><span style="font-size: 16pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;" lang="EN-US"></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 18pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;" lang="EN-US">1.</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">组成：<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 18pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">该漆由两组份分装，甲组份为固化化剂，乙组份为环氧树脂、防锈、防腐颜料经耐磨分散而成。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 18pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;" lang="EN-US">2.</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">特性：<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 18pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">漆膜干燥迅速，具有附着力好，硬度高持久优异的耐腐蚀性，特别对于潮湿环境中的大型设施，以及除锈不完全的装置涂料更为适用，该漆利用涂料对锈层的湿润渗透，把铁锈分隔包围在涂料中，使之成为漆膜的一部分，阻止锈蚀的发展，原漆有固体份高而粘度低施工简便的特点。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 18pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;" lang="EN-US">3.</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">用途：<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 18pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">主要用于桥梁、井架、贮罐、集装箱、内河船舶等大型钢铁制品的底层涂装。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style