N-US">3</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">、一次喷涂不要太厚，以避免流挂和产生弊病，如需较厚的漆膜应分几次喷涂，每次间隔<span lang="EN-US">5-10 min</span>。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 44.7pt; text-indent: -20.75pt; line-height: 28pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;" lang="EN-US">4</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">、可采用湿碰湿工艺喷涂，但若第一层漆已完全干透，则应先用细沙纸稍加打磨再施工，以便提高层间附着性。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 44.7pt; text-indent: -20.75pt; line-height: 28pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;" lang="EN-US">5</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">、喷涂完毕后，流平时间<span lang="EN-US">5-10 min</span>，再进行烘干。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 44.7pt; text-indent: -20.75pt; line-height: 28pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;" lang="EN-US">6</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">、包装桶内剩余的漆应立即加盖密封，以防污染的吸潮，特别是固化剂用后应随时密封，否则会导致胶凝失效。</span></p>', '各色丙烯酸聚氨酯磁漆', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '22-revision-4', '', '', '2009-04-12 18:31:10', '2009-04-12 10:31:10', '', 22, 'http://herun/productions/22-revision-4/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
