 	mso-padding-alt:0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; 	mso-border-insideh:.5pt solid windowtext; 	mso-border-insidev:.5pt solid windowtext; 	mso-para-margin:0cm; 	mso-para-margin-bottom:.0001pt; 	text-align:justify; 	text-justify:inter-ideograph; 	mso-pagination:none; 	font-size:10.0pt; 	font-family:"Times New Roman"; 	mso-ansi-language:#0400; 	mso-fareast-language:#0400; 	mso-bidi-language:#0400;} -->\r\n\r\n<!--[endif]-->\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 18pt;"></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 18pt;"><a href="http://herun/wp-content/uploads/2009/04/e5ad99e4b8bde8908d-045_resize.jpg"><img class="alignnone size-full wp-image-25" title="e5ad99e4b8bde8908d-045_resize" src="http://herun/wp-content/uploads/2009/04/e5ad99e4b8bde8908d-045_resize.jpg" alt="e5ad99e4b8bde8908d-045_resize" width="480" height="360" /></a></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 18pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">一、产品概述：</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 18pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;" lang="EN-US">1.</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">组成：</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 18pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">该漆由两组份分装，甲组份为固化化剂，乙组份为环氧树脂、防锈、防腐颜料经耐磨分散而成。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 18pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;" lang="EN-US">2.</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">特性：</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 18pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">漆膜干燥迅速，具有附着力好，硬度高持久优异的耐腐蚀性，特别对于潮湿环境中的大型设施，以及除锈不完全的装置涂料更为适用，该漆利用涂料对锈层的湿润渗透，把铁锈分隔包围在涂料中，使之成为漆膜的一部分，阻止锈蚀的发展，原漆有固体份高而粘度低施工简便的特点。</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 18pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;"><!--more-->\r\n</span>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 18pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;" lang="EN-US">3.</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">用途：</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 27pt; line-height: 18pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">主要用于桥梁、井架、贮罐、集装箱、内河船舶等大型钢铁制品的底层涂装。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 18pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">二、产品技术指标：</span></p>\r\n\r\n<table class="MsoTableGrid" style="border: medium none; border-collapse: collapse;" border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr style="height: 4.25pt;">\r\n<td style="border: 1pt solid windowtext; padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 167.15pt; height: 4.25pt;" width="223">\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center; line-height: 12pt;" align="center"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">项<span lang="EN-US"><span> </span></span>目</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 170.75pt; height: 4.25pt;" width="228">\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center; line-height: 12pt;" align="center"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">指<span lang="EN-US"><span> </span><span> </span></span>标</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 81.6pt; height: 4.25pt;" width="109">\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center; line-height: 12pt;" align="center"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">试验方法</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr style="height: 36.45pt;">\r\n<td style="padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 167.15pt; height: 36.45pt;" width="223">\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">漆膜颜色外观</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 170.75pt; height: 36.45pt;" width="228">\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">色调不定、平整光滑</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: