/span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 42.05pt; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: 20pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;" lang="EN-US">1.</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">被涂物件应预先除油污等其它污染物，如需取得更好的耐化学品质，须经磷化和喷涂环氧底漆。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 42.05pt; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: 20pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;" lang="EN-US">2.</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">配漆时，应将原漆搅拌均匀，并加入适量的稀释剂；如果用静电喷涂需用静电稀释剂，喷涂粘度<span lang="EN-US">18</span>～<span lang="EN-US">25s/25<span lang="EN-US"><span lang="EN-US">℃</span></span><span lang="EN-US">（25<span lang="EN-US"><span lang="EN-US">℃</span></span>-4</span></span>）为宜。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 42.05pt; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: 20pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;" lang="EN-US">3.</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">喷涂后需静置<span lang="EN-US">15min</span>以上，再进入烘房烘烤，烘烤温度视工件材质厚薄可适当调整。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 42.05pt; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: 20pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;" lang="EN-US">4.</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">本漆贮存期为半年。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>', '各色氨基烘干磁漆', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '76-revision-2', '', '', '2009-04-15 15:17:33', '2009-04-15 07:17:33', '', 76, 'http://herun/?p=78', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
