moz-use-text-color windowtext windowtext -moz-use-text-color;" width="120">\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center; line-height: 12pt;" align="center"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">分夏季、冬季<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody></table>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 28pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">四、施工工艺<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 44.7pt; text-indent: -20.75pt; line-height: 28pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;" lang="EN-US">1</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">、先将乙组份充分搅拌均匀，以避免颜色光泽的差异。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 44.7pt; text-indent: -20.75pt; line-height: 28pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;" lang="EN-US">2</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">、将甲、乙两组份按比例混合均匀，再用专用稀释剂将漆液粘度调整到<span lang="EN-US">18</span>—<span lang="EN-US">22S</span>（涂—<span lang="EN-US">4</span>，<span lang="EN-US">25</span>℃），用<span lang="EN-US">200-300</span>目铜丝网过滤后在室温下放置<span lang="EN-US">10-20 min,</span>待漆液中气泡基本消失后再进行喷涂。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 44.7pt; text-indent: -20.75pt; line-height: 28pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;" lang="EN-US">3</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">、一次喷涂不要太厚，以避免流挂和产生弊病，如需较厚的漆膜应分几次喷涂，每次间隔<span lang="EN-US">5-10 min</span>。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 44.7pt; text-indent: -20.75pt; line-height: 28pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;" lang="EN-US">4</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">、可采用湿碰湿工艺喷涂，但若第一层漆已完全干透，则应先用细沙纸稍加打磨再施工，以便提高层间附着性。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 44.7pt; text-indent: -20.75pt; line-height: 28pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;" lang="EN-US">5</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">、喷涂完毕后，流平时间<span lang="EN-US">5-10 min</span>，再进行烘干。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;" lang="EN-US">6</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">、包装桶内剩余的漆应立即加盖密封，以防污染的吸潮，特别是固化剂用后应随时密封，否则会导致胶凝失效。</span>', '各色丙烯酸聚氨酯磁漆', 0, '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '22-revision-13', '', '', '2009-04-15 23:13:45', '2009-04-15 15:13:45', '', 22, 'http://herun/?p=126', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
