-US">8</span></span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;" lang="EN-US">h</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;">）</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td style="padding: 0cm 5.4pt; width: 212.8pt;" width="284" valign="top">\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center; line-height: 18pt;" align="center"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">允许轻微失光，变白，小泡能于<span lang="EN-US">3</span>小时内恢复，不起泡不起皱允许失光，<span lang="EN-US">1</span>小时内恢复。</span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody></table>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 22pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">三、施工参考：</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 42.05pt; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: 22pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;" lang="EN-US">1</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">、喷涂或刷涂均可，能常温干燥，但在<span lang="EN-US">60-70<span lang="EN-US"><span lang="EN-US">℃</span></span><span lang="EN-US">干燥漆膜性能更好，漆膜不宜涂刷过厚，为了获得丰满的漆膜，可涂2-3</span></span>道，但必须在第一道完全干燥后才能涂第二道。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 42.05pt; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: 22pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;" lang="EN-US">2</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">、配套要求可先涂<span lang="EN-US">1-2</span>道<span lang="EN-US">C06-1</span>铁红醇酸底漆，用醇酸腻子补平喷涂时先将原漆搅拌均匀，再用专用稀释剂（<span lang="EN-US">X-6</span>）调整施工粘度。</span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 42.05pt; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: 22pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;" lang="EN-US">3</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">、存期为半年，超过贮存期，可按标准规定的项目进行检查，如结果符合要求，仍可使用。</span></p>', '各色醇酸磁漆', 0, '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '70-revision-4', '', '', '2009-04-15 23:04:48', '2009-04-15 15:04:48', '', 70, 'http://herun/?p=134', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
