e solid solid none -moz-use-text-color windowtext windowtext -moz-use-text-color;" width="189" valign="top">\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">氟碳清漆<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;" lang="EN-US">1</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">：<span lang="EN-US">11</span></span></p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<!--[if !supportMisalignedColumns]-->\r\n<tr height="0">\r\n<td style="border: medium none;" width="189"></td>\r\n<td style="border: medium none;" width="95"></td>\r\n<td style="border: medium none;" width="95"></td>\r\n<td style="border: medium none;" width="189"></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<!--[endif]--></tbody></table>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 23pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">备注：具体颜色的氟碳涂料甲组分与乙组分的配漆比例以包装上标识为准。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 23pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;" lang="EN-US">2</span><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">、施工技术，操作要点<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 41.95pt; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: 23pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">※ 打开包装桶盖后，首先检查原漆流动性是否正常（若有异常禁止使用），充分搅拌均匀桶内涂料。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 41.95pt; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: 23pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">※ 将甲、乙组分按规定的配比准备称取好并充分搅拌均匀，应做到现用现配，用多少配多劳多少，在<span lang="EN-US">8</span>小时内用完。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 23pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">※ 配好的漆用<span lang="EN-US">80</span>—<span lang="EN-US">120</span>目铜丝布过滤，放置换<span lang="EN-US">30</span>分钟后再使用。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 41.95pt; text-indent: -18pt; line-height: 23pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">※ 根据所选用的施工方法，用氟碳涂料专用稀释剂调整施工粘度，稀释剂用量控制在案<span lang="EN-US">10-30%</span>。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 23pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">※ 未用完的漆应立即盖紧包装盖，并应在产品有限期内使用完。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 23pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">四、施工中可能出现的异常控制<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 89.95pt; text-indent: -66pt; line-height: 23pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">※ 刷<span lang="EN-US"><span> </span></span>痕：本漆在刷涂时，严禁粘度过大或施工温度过高，否则导致刷痕的产生。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 89.95pt; text-indent: -66pt; line-height: 23pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">※ 缩<span lang="EN-US"><span> </span></span>孔：本漆在施工时，严禁底材有油污或漆液被油污染，否则易导致气泡的产生。对墙体基层封闭不完全都可能导致气泡产生。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 23pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">※ 干燥过慢：温度过低时施工，会延长漆膜干燥时间。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>\r\n<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-indent: 24pt; line-height: 23pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">※ 有雨、雾、霜冻、刮大风天气不宜施工。<span lang="EN-US"></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: 楷体_GB2312;">※ 被涂物表面温度必须高于露点<span lang="EN-US">3</span>℃以上才可以施工。</span>', '各色氟碳树脂磁漆（分装）、氟碳树脂清漆（分装）', 0, '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '17-revision-9', '', '', '2009-04-15 23:25:30', '2009-04-15 15:25:30', '', 17, 'http://herun/?p=199', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
